<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>UNITE - Supervisor - User Deactivation</title>
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <meta name="description" content="A cool thing made with Glitch">
  <link id="favicon" rel="icon" href="https://glitch.com/edit/favicon-app.ico" type="image/x-icon">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/messages.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/jquery-ui.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/bootstrap.min.css">
  <script src="/jquery.min.js"></script>
  <script src="/jquery-ui.min.js"></script>
  <script src="/popper.min.js"></script>
  <script src="/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
  <script src="/sweetalert2@9.min.js"></script>
  <script src="/https.js"></script>  
  <script src="/functions.js"></script>
  <script type="text/javascript">
    $(document).ready(function() {
      errorSuccess(Swal, '<%= errorMessage %>', '<%= successMessage %>');
      
      $('#mainForm').submit(function(e) {
        if(!confirm('Are you sure you want to deactivate your Buyer account?\nThis will remove your placed Bid Requests in UNITE. You will be automatically reactivated at the next login.\nWe hope to see you back soon!')) {
          return false;
        }
      });
    });
  </script>
</head>

<body>
  <nav user="buyer" class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark" style="width: 100% !important;">
    <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">UNITE - Deactivate Supervisor Account</a>
    <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbarSupportedContent"
      aria-controls="navbarSupportedContent" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
      <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
    </button>
  </nav>
    <div class="container">
       <div class="col-md-12">
        <form id="mainForm" action="/supervisor/deactivate/<%= id %>" method="POST">
          <legend>
            Deactivate Supervisor Account - Please fill in the required (*) fields
          </legend>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="email">E-mail*:</label>
            <input required class="form-control" type="email" name="emailAddress" autofocus="autofocus"></input>
          </div>
         <div class="form-group">
            <label for="email">Organization name*:</label>
            <input required class="form-control" type="text" name="organizationName"></input>
           <input type="hidden" name="id" value="<%= id %>">
            <input type="hidden" name="uniteID" value="<%= uniteId %>">
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="reason">Reason for deactivating account*:</label>
            <textarea required class="form-control" id="reason" name="reason"></textarea>
          </div>
          <input type="hidden" name="type" value="User Deactivation">          
          <input type="hidden" name="userType" value="Supervisor">
          <div class="form-group">
            <input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="<%= csrfToken %>">
            <button type="submit" id="deactivate" title="Deactivate Account" class="btn btn-primary btn-block btn-lg">Deactivate Account</button>
            <br>
          <div class="form-group text-center">
            <textarea cols="40" rows="8" disabled style="color: green; font-family: arial; font-size: 14pt">
If you choose to temporarily deactivate your Supervisor Account, please make sure you have no active Buyers on UNITE. It is not recommended to leave your corresponding Buyers without any surveillance/supervising upon them. Doing so may encourage them to engage in unlawful activities, so please consider making this decision very carefully.
            </textarea>
          </div>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>